quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  98,1,"Abagararije mu bahawe Igitabu no mu babangikanyamana, ntibari kugera aho bavavanura n’ubugarariji, kugeza bashikiriwe n’icemeza kiboneka;"
  98,2,"Ico cemeza, ni Intumwa ivuye ku Mana Allah, yaje ibasomera Qor’ani yanditswe ku mpapuro zitagiramwo agasembwa, zisukuye."
  98,3,"Harimwo ibimenyetso n’amategeko atomoye, arongora mu nzira igororotse."
  98,4,"Abahawe Igitabu, ntibiciyemwo imigwi ku vyerekeye ukwemera umuzo w’Intumwa Muhamadi, kiretse inyuma y’aho bashikiriwe n’icemeza kiboneka, cemeza ko Muhamadi (nyakugira amahoro n’impuhwe z’Imana), ari yo Ntumwa y’Imana Allah basezeraniwe mu Bitabu vyabo."
  98,5,"Nta n’ikindi bategetswe gukora mu mabwirizwa bahawe, atari ukwiyegereza Imana Allah mu vyo bakora vyose banayisenga ari Imwe Rudende, beze idini ryayo batayibangikanya, batsimbataze n’amasengesho ku mwanya, banatange n’ishikanwa-bwirizwa. Iryo rero, ni ryo dini ry’ukuri, ni na bwo bwislamu."
  98,6,"Mu vy’ukuri, abagararije mu bahawe Igitabu n’ababangikanyamana, bazohanwa mu muriro wa Jahannamu, bazowubamwo ibihe bidahera. Abo rero, ni bo babi cane mu biremwa."
  98,7,"Mu vy’ukuri, abemeye Imana Allah n’Intumwa yayo bagakora n’ivyiza bitegetswe; abo rero, ni bo beza cane mu biremwa;"
  98,8,"Impembo yabo ku Mana yabo Rurema Allah, ni imirima itotahaye yo mu Bwami bw’ijuru rya “Adeni”, musi y’inyubakwa n’ibiti vyabwo hatemba inzuzi, bazobubamwo ibihe bidahera, mu nema zamaho. Imana Allah Yarabashimiye ku vyo bakoze, na bo nyene barayishimiye ku mpera Yabageneye. Iyo, ni yo mpembo y’uwatinye gucumura ku Mana yiwe Rurema Allah."
